Oh, you've got to get that away from me.

01:08:22.912 --> 01:08:27.679
Can they see it?

01:08:27.679 --> 01:08:28.799
Yeah.

01:08:28.799 --> 01:08:38.872
That's too hot; I don't even touch it.

01:08:38.872 --> 01:08:44.734
That's what it looks like.

01:08:44.734 --> 01:08:47.839
Well, you did great.

01:08:47.839 --> 01:08:50.125
Can you just help me pray?

01:08:50.125 --> 01:08:50.696
Yes.

01:09:05.199 --> 01:09:05.419
That smells good.

01:09:05.419 --> 01:09:12.309
Oh, Paisley, I sure love you.

01:09:12.319 --> 01:09:14.498
I love you too, Daddy.

01:09:14.498 --> 01:09:18.780
She knows that's my weakness.

01:09:18.780 --> 01:09:28.182
I told her to give those brownies away.

01:09:28.182 --> 01:09:30.879
Father, I thank you, Lord.

01:09:30.879 --> 01:09:32.920
I pray over her.

01:09:32.920 --> 01:09:36.860
Father, I thank you, Lord, for this time.

01:09:36.860 --> 01:09:40.159
Who wants to go tubing?

01:09:40.159 --> 01:09:45.000
