01:09:45.000 --> 01:09:49.680
You're here, so let's go.

01:10:29.177 --> 01:10:30.023
I haven't done it in a while, so I feel rested more than the last two days.

01:10:35.759 --> 01:10:36.557
It was rough.

01:11:19.199 --> 01:11:20.189
Oh, Father, we thank you, Lord, for your blood.

01:11:20.189 --> 01:11:52.318
