You know, if it were on a soft key, that's the temperament right now.

01:53:29.749 --> 01:53:33.227
You feel that?

01:53:34.800 --> 01:53:36.311
It's that still small voice.

01:53:36.311 --> 01:53:37.813
It's not loud.

01:53:37.813 --> 01:53:46.177
Especially the mood for tonight; I can feel it.

01:54:04.853 --> 01:54:05.226
It's down here, in the lower octave.

01:54:05.226 --> 01:54:08.800
It's a very small, lower key.

01:54:08.800 --> 01:54:29.778
This is what I hear: there are so many of you that are like on a racetrack.

01:54:29.778 --> 01:54:48.075
You're going as fast as you can with life.

01:54:48.075 --> 01:55:39.408
